# NOTICE

This file contains attribution notices for third-party software included in Easel.

NOTICE: This file is generated at build time using the `npm run notice` command,
which scans node_modules and extracts license information from package.json files.

The generated NOTICE will include:
  - Component Name
  - Version
  - License
  - Repository URL (if available)

To regenerate this file locally, run:
  npm run notice

To regenerate the SBOM (Software Bill of Materials), run:
  npm run sbom

Both commands are executed automatically during the release workflow (see .github/workflows/release.yml).
